qotd - Quote of the Day Server Implementation
=============================================
qotd is an implementation of the rfc 865.

Requirements
------------
You need a sane operating system to be able to build qotd.

Installation
------------
Edit config.mk to match your local setup and run `make clean install`

Running qotd
------------
You must pass the command to be executed by qotd to renew the quote in argument
of the program.

	$ qotd fortune

For example to have on fortume a day.

Configuration
-------------

The configuration of qotd can be done inside config.mk in order to change the
renewal time of the quotes.

